TWEET: everytime you meditate, or repeat a new affirmation, or visualize a new possibility for 1 minute, you start the process of firing new neural pathways and rewiring your brain. yes, it's simple, but the magic is in the consistency. repetition is medicine for the brain.
REPLY: Sa yathā kāmo bhavati, tat kratur bhavati; yat kratur bhavati tat karma kurute; yat karma kurute tad abhisaṃpadyate. — Bṛhadāraṇyaka Upaniṣad (4.4.5)
As one's intention becomes, so does one's resolve; as the resolve, so the action; as the action, so the result one becomes.

